  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="Aink101-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">
            tāykku uraitta pattu </p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
The ten that was narrated to the Mother
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Aink101">
            <lg type="edition">
              <l> aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai yutukkā </l>
              <l> ṇērkoṭip pācaṭumpu pariyavūr piḻipu</l>
                        <l> neytaṉ mayakki vantaṉṟu niṉmakaḷ</l>
                        <l> pūppō luṇkaṇ marīiya</l>
                        <l> nōykkumarun tākiya koṇkaṉ ṟērē </l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh Mother! (Listen) with desire Mother! Look there - </l>
<l> Tearing up the green Aṭumpu's superior creepers, rising and falling </l>
<l> Making the Neytal fade </l>
<l> The chariot of the Lord of the seashore </l>
<l> That is the antidote to the affliction that is set into </l>
<l> The kohl-rimmed flower-like eyes of your daughter </l>
<l> Has arrived. </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
